features.text:
#Eliminating counterparty risk

Wrapped Token Vaults are immutable, publicly owned, and free to use by anyone. Automating the issuance of relational wrapped tokens by the Vault contract eliminates the ability of token theft. This evolution of blockchain technology ensures the integrity of issued wrapped tokens as each digital asset contained in the vault can be individually audited.

#Automatic token wrapping

Vaults issue specific tokens whenever an NFT is deposited. Since these can be exchanged at a set ratio with any deposited NFT, the combined value of all tokens in circulation matches the combined value of all deposited NFTs

#By: Bittrees, Inc.



#Digital Vaults are building blocks

Vaults are fundamental building blocks in modern digital finance. Wrapped Token Vaults create inherent, recursive relationships between related non-fungible and fungible tokens. As compared to other vault protocols, the process of issuing a relational wrapped token is automated by the Vault contract and therefore eliminates counterparty risk. This elegant solution simplifies the process of unlocking liquidity from non-fungible digital assets.

# What's the point of wrapped tokens?

Wrapped token holders can redeem one wToken for any NFT in a LP.

Swapping one basic wrapped token for another becomes a trivial task compared to negotiating a trade with another user.

Buying and selling NFTs in bulk is straightforward. There is Uniswap - using a liquidity pool - where traders buy and sell dozens of wrapped token credits at once.

These redemption, "credit tokens" can be offered to holders at a lower cost than creating new NFTs.

# And the basket is fully – and beautifully – transparent.

#Fractionalization
1 Deploy a vault with a non 1:1 fractionalization ratio.

 2 (Recommended) configure the vault to only accept a single NFT.
#Index Funds
1 Configure a vault to only accept a specific range of NFTs.

2 Restrict the vault to prevent withdrawals.


#Museum Vault
1 Restrict the vault to prevent withdrawals.

2 (Optionally) Remove all admins.

#NFT Swaps
1 Configure a vault to only accept two NFTs.


2 Deposit NFT A.

3 The other party will deposit NFT B and withdraw NFT A with their newly issued parity token.

4 Withdraw NFT B.
